Sidebar
- Collapsible widths: 14 (collapsed) / 56 (expanded); sticky and backdrop-blurred.
- Mobile overlay closes on route change and `Esc`.

Navigation
- Source nav items from `src/constants/navigation.tsx`; avoid hardcoding.
- Use `usePathname()` to determine active state.

Command palette
- Keep actions idempotent; avoid side effects that conflict with router prefetch.

